📌 Overview

This section documents the implementation of:

Alerting using Prometheus Alertmanager
Logging using Loki + Promtail

The goal is to move from:

Monitoring → knowing what is happening

to:

Alerting → knowing when something is wrong  
Logging → knowing why it went wrong
